home.blog_description: Important announcements and news about April bot, including new releases and new commands
home.commands_description: Useful information about April commands and how to correctly use them
home.feature_analytics_description: Powerful data to help grow your server
home.feature_log_description: Know everything that happened in your server
home.feature_selfrole_description: Allow user to self assign role
home.intro_analytics_description: April gives you the tools to monitor your server. View how many user have joined/left today or one month ago, know how many of them have return, know who is the most active user and much more.
home.intro_footer_description: A lot of more services are included to help you maximize the productivity of your server
home.intro_image_editor_description: Design your own welcomer images to give to your new users a radiant welcome or choose from a wide range of pre-made images on the marketplace
home.intro_invite_title: Invite April Bot now and start using it's fantastic features
home.intro_reaction_role_description: Create powerful reaction roles with different combinations available, each reaction will do what you exactly what it to do. Finally, easily create and manage your reaction role with just a few clicks.
home.marketplace_description: Create and share your creativity with other users
home.premium_benefits_description: As a thank you for your support maintaining the cost of running April your selected guild will receive some benefits while using April, check out below to view all of them.
home.premium_description: Important announcements and news about April bot, including new releases and new commands
home.premium_feature_additional_credit_d: In addition to the 100 daily credits, you'll get 400 more credits for a total of 500 daily credits
home.premium_feature_ads_free_descriptio: Any server member that visits the dashboard will no longer see any ads, limited only for the servers who have premium
home.premium_feature_analytics_descripti: Forget about the limit of 7 days history and see your full history or customize the dates and see the history of that time frame
home.premium_feature_high_quality_image_: Welcome/leaver elements will be optimized on the end to produce a high quality image (can add some seconds of delay)
home.premium_feature_no_ads_description: You'll no more see any ads in any part of the website while you're logged with your premium account
home.premium_feature_no_limit_descriptio: All the limits for the server will be gone, you will be able to add as many Autorole, Reaction Role, Custom command etc as you want
home.premium_feature_upload_description: You'll be able to upload image up to 10mb for your welcomer/leaver image
home.premium_thank_you_description: You will be helping April development cost such as VPS, website server and domains. Finally, to deliver more features
home.premium_user_benefits_description: In addition to the above list, the user who pay for the subscribe will receive some exclusive benefits listed below.
